<html><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"><meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no" name="viewport"><link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="_TheLordTitlesAndRL.css" /></head><body>

<div class="c230_124"> 
<div id="v230.124.1"><span class="H7892 s">A Song</span><span class="H4609 s"> of degrees</span><span class="H1732 s"> of David</span><span class="H3884 s">. If</span><span class="H3068 s"> <i>it had not been</i> the LORD</span><span class="H3478 s"> who was on our side, now may Israel</span><span class="H559 s"> say</span>;</div> 
<div id="v230.124.2"><span class="H3884 s">If</span><span class="H3068 s"> <i>it had not been</i> the LORD</span><span class="H120 s"> who was on our side, when men</span><span class="H6965 s"> rose up</span> against us:</div> 
<div id="v230.124.3"><span class="H233 s">Then</span><span class="H1104 s"> they had swallowed us up</span><span class="H2416 s"> quick</span><span class="H639 s">, when their wrath</span><span class="H2734 s"> was kindled</span> against us:</div> 
<div id="v230.124.4"><span class="H233 s">Then</span><span class="H4325 s"> the waters</span><span class="H7857 s"> had overwhelmed</span><span class="H5158 s"> us, the stream</span><span class="H5674 s"> had gone over</span><span class="H5315 s"> our soul</span>:</div> 
<div id="v230.124.5"><span class="H233 s">Then</span><span class="H2121 s"> the proud</span><span class="H4325 s"> waters</span><span class="H5674 s"> had gone over</span><span class="H5315 s"> our soul</span>.</div> 
<div id="v230.124.6"><span class="H1288 s">Blessed</span><span class="H3068 s"> <i>be</i> the LORD</span><span class="H5414 s">, who hath not given</span><span class="H2964 s"> us <i>as</i> a prey</span><span class="H8127 s"> to their teeth</span>.</div> 
<div id="v230.124.7"><span class="H5315 s">Our soul</span><span class="H4422 s"> is escaped</span><span class="H6833 s"> as a bird</span><span class="H6341 s"> out of the snare</span><span class="H3369 s"> of the fowlers</span><span class="H6341 s">: the snare</span><span class="H7665 s"> is broken</span><span class="H4422 s">, and we are escaped</span>.</div> 
<div id="v230.124.8"><span class="H5828 s">Our help</span><span class="H8034 s"> <i>is</i> in the name</span><span class="H3068 s"> of the LORD</span><span class="H6213 s">, who made</span><span class="H8064 s"> heaven</span><span class="H776 s"> and earth</span>.</div></div>

